Terraform + Ansible Monitoring Stack + Host a Site (Nginx + Prometheus + Grafana) :
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Project Overview:
-----------------

This project demonstrates a real-time DevOps infrastructure using:

    -->Terraform → Infrastructure provisioning (AWS)
    --?Ansible → Configuration management
    -->Nginx → Web server
    -->Prometheus → Metrics collection
    -->Grafana → Visualization dashboards
    -->Node Exporter + Nginx Exporter + Blackbox Exporter→ Monitoring data

 Architecture:
--------------

2 EC2 Instances:

    -->Web Server
    -->Nginx
    -->Node Exporter
    -->Nginx Exporter
    -->Domain: tech.dovin.xyz

Monitoring Server:

    -->Prometheus
    -->Grafana
    -->Dashboards

